info: GXO Logistics, Inc. provides supply chain management solutions for multinational companies and blue-chip market leaders worldwide. It serves consumer packaged goods, ecommerce, food and beverage, retail, technology, and consume electronic industries. The company was incorporated in 2021 and is based in Greenwich, Connecticut. GXO Logistics, Inc. operates independently of XPO Logistics, Inc. as of August 2, 2021.
